2 officers have been reported to have been knocked down by a bus driving against traffic. The bus driver was stopped but he suddenly zoomed and hit the two officers who are currently in the hospital with multiple fractures and head injuries.  Reports Read: “I am heartbroken,half an hour ago.2 officers👮🏿👮🏾‍♀️on duty on 3MBridge were knocked down by a bus driving against traffic.They flagged him down he stopped n suddenly he zoomed and hit d men.officers rushed 2 Hosp,multiple fractures &head injuries diagnosed.Bus recovered, Drvr bolted” Source